  <front>
   <head>[Epitaph on a Child]</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="sestet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Here, freed from pain, secure from misery, lies</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A child, the darling of his parents' eyes:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A gentler lamb ne'er sported on the plain,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A fairer flower will never bloom again.</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Few were the days allotted to his breath;</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Now let him sleep in peace his night of death.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
